### GET /channels/{name}
Returns channel by name.

**Response (200):**
```json
{
  "name": "string",
  "channelType": "QUEUE" | "STREAM",
  "routingKeys": ["string"],
  "consumptionType": "STANDARD" | "FIFO" | null,
  "routingKeysCircuitState": [
    {
      "routingKey": "string",
      "circuitState": "CLOSED" | "OPEN"
    }
  ]
}
```

**Response (404):** Channel not found

